{"tid":2237871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地繼續送$比人啦～～～～～～～","createTime":"2020-10-10T15:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T18:01:28.000Z","uid":340703,"like":107,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"575a64389f2af82c12d37a596a1fbabca0fa705e","tid":2237871,"uid":340703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺茶半香初做過一排，入去做之前喺facebook見到間野好黃，做落先知個姓陳既老闆根本偽黃熱狗，借個黃圈賺錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友話自己d飲品新鮮製造，其實全部都made in支那，元素週期表扮新鮮製造。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母d生果放撚到生蟲仲整俾人飲，有同事講過不如掉左佢驚飲壞人，個老細孤寒兼縮骨，話照賣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZkuZO6S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZkuZO6S.jpg&h=8673a237&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WtDkdy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WtDkdy.jpg&h=2cba91ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個基金我見有ching都有講，終於有人醒起佢個濕鳩基金如屎救援。佢個基金同肛榮個老細一齊搞，內部數目混亂，claim錢又冇單，完全私人銀行咁，大家唔信既即管睇下佢地敢唔敢公開盤數，拎唔拎到單出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dac484a8c55ddf600bf5f7e987ee2939a81bd7","tid":2237871,"uid":340703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f6f7fc4846cd6d23258fba69ef6d8dd38baf4d","tid":2237871,"uid":340703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ddffa88787311d34bd822e9b361bc0bd47d61c","tid":2237871,"uid":340703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"大家推啊～～～～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7731fa544239424e3b78488c47b12e4c309bfb32","tid":2237871,"uid":340703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b4fe927a29f0c879e9b08687771b353a44cdc3","tid":2237871,"uid":340703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi