r />\nching琴日喺隔離post係咪話都有野爆"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"早喺武肺爆發初期，全城鬧口罩荒，茶半香初就同光榮個老細搞左個賣口罩。當時俾佢搵到批口罩，成本價大概60幾蚊盒，當佢連埋運費乜乜柒柒應該100蚊盒。但佢同人講成本價已經180幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲用塊牌寫住憑良心出價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢個「憑良心」果然好有效，好多人真係幾百幾百咁塞俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。連我d朋友都俾左1500蚊買3盒（質素仲要極差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。喺呢次既情緒勒索，道德綁架「派」口罩活動入面，陳先生總共賺左50幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。然後佢開始覺得背負住個光環同客源單一化根本唔可以賺太多，既然搵到貨緊係要賺到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以佢第二批貨唔打算以茶半香初既名義賣，佢決定匿名炒口罩。唔知係咪天有眼定係佢太心急，佢竟然俾人黑食黑呃返佢轉頭。佢落既訂金俾人呃晒，錢又冇貨又冇。但係佢好醒，即刻化危為機，佢即刻喺facebook同ig同大家講佢為大家訂既第2批口罩俾人呃，好慘慘豬，扮為大家付出就算俾人呃都唔介意得嚟又不乏叫春。果然大家即刻好受落，話要去懲罰佢幫佢填返條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"f2cd0e7563ba9c60a4c43c2bec53c61165e47393","tid":2237871,"uid":340703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b84d49114ca6c7b380bc5788f5087454f0b8d4d1","tid":2237871,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"借ac 出post 求其改 體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd4c5ccafef450f756dfae4a1b65d8ccba729bf","tid":2237871,"uid":57151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe15dbde2d51d7ec856f603719847